 data, the purposes for which we process your personal data and whether we can achieve those purposes through other means, and the applicable legal requirements.","If you would like to access, update, or delete any information we have about you, or exercise any right you might have, please use the Delete Account option within the app or contact us at itsupport@appolonia.ae"]
